playstore_details.title: ARCON Authenticator
playstore_details.description: Privileged account access requires a well established identity references (validation) for users accessing critical IT components. ARCON Authenticator provides a robust validation mechanism. The solution's MFA functionality acts a strategic entry point to identity management systems and helps managing system based users.
